{"tid":1357550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【外國勢力】美國國會中國委員會主席拍片講元朗事件","createTime":"2019-07-23T17:47:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T18:32:41.000Z","uid":27797,"like":60,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"daaf19cbf4c8190b53f942b82b50a2bbe1a0e5a0","tid":1357550,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T17:47:01.000Z","msg":"竟然無人開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黃之鋒Facebook: 佛羅里達州參議員、 Congressional-Executive Commission on China 兩位主席之一 Marco Rubio 拍攝短片，向美國人講述週末在元朗發生的襲擊事件。他直指中國共產黨在香港支持有黑社會背景的暴徒追打和平示威者，以至是其他的路人，正好反映中國政府的本質，並呼籲全球一起予以譴責。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/200976479994868/posts/2380130648746096?s=1687043028&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F200976479994868%2Fposts%2F2380130648746096%3Fs%3D1687043028%26sfns%3Dmo&d=usS1U3EkKACzPkxZ%2FEkdU%2Bbr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=36a2f59e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/200976479994868/posts/2380130648746096?s=1687043028&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"5b1d068ea1412a06e4709b5c802e9aa9106bc521","tid":1357550,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T17:47:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"52630998544e4db2f5d423163be16c9053e1010b","tid":1357550,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T17:48:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3f50dd5e490af252afddee722b6efb2b01fc5eda","tid":1357550,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T17:50:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ae87dc9473de4f7ccc196f544963778307b9a3c6","tid":1357550,"uid":94484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T17:50:19.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"5d282951dc0a605168d70aa2465e144f5edc7936","tid":1357550,"uid":168169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T17:50:43.000Z","msg":"燒到去中共何妖真係插翼難飛"},{"pid":"fbe7ff4bf290d08714400e600691bcc6a